{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/lightnovel-id-comic-frontier-11/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"LightNovel.ID Pamerkan Light Novel Lokal di Comic Frontier 11","content":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Comic Frontier kembali hadir untuk yang kesebelas kalinya. Sama seperti beberapa kesempatan terakhirnya, Comic Frontier 11 kali ini diadakan di Kartika Expo pada 18-19 Agustus 2018 mendatang. Dalam acara ini, komunitas Light Novel dan Novel Ringan Indonesia—atau yang singkatnya disebut LightNovel.ID — kembali berkesempatan turut meramaikan acara.</p>\n<p>Pada kesempatan kali ini, LightNovel.ID turut menggelar booth di circle booth nomor 19 (CB19) di mana selain ada presentasi karya terbarunya tahun ini, LightNovel.ID juga menemani Wibuverse— startup baru di mana kreator bisa menjajakan karya-karyanya secara digital dan tanpa diperantarai oleh pihak ketiga.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/meriahnya-comic-frontier-x-bersama-ciayo-comics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Meriahnya Comic Frontier X Bersama CIAYO Comics</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49875\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49875\" data-attachment-id=\"49875\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lightnovel-id-comic-frontier-11/attachment/01-lightnovel-id-cf11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-lightnovel.id-cf11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49875 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" alt=\"LightNovel.ID comifuro 11\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49875\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: LightNovel.ID</p></div></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Di sini, LightNovel.ID akan menjajakan karya-karya terbarunya. Dari beberapa pengisi ekshibisi dari LightNovel.ID, sudah dipastikan akan menjadi sorotan utama di kolom pegiat novel ringan Indonesia ini. Beberapa di antaranya adalah sebagai berikut.</p>\n<h2>Jajaran Light Novel Terbitan LightNovel.ID di Comic Frontier 11</h2>\n<h3>Everna Saga</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49876\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49876\" data-attachment-id=\"49876\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lightnovel-id-comic-frontier-11/attachment/02-lightnovel-id-cf11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-lightnovel.id-cf11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49876 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" alt=\"LightNovel.ID everna saga\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49876\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: LightNovel.ID</p></div></p>\n<p>Everna Saga adalah cerita-cerita fantasi epik bernuansa aksi dan petualangan karangan Andry Chang. Menceritakan tentang Robert Chandler, seorang pemburu yang seringkali terlibat dengan peristiwa-peristiwa besar yang terjadi di Everna. Everna Saga sudah berlangsung sepanjang tiga jilid.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/kiat-kiat-dari-andry-chang-juara-3-ciayo-short-story-challenge/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kiat-kiat Dari Andry Chang, Juara 3 CIAYO Short Story Challenge</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Eternal Dimension</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49877\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49877\" data-attachment-id=\"49877\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lightnovel-id-comic-frontier-11/attachment/03-lightnovel-id-cf11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-lightnovel.id-cf11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49877 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" alt=\"LightNovel.ID eternal dimension\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49877\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: LightNovel.ID</p></div></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Eternal Dimension jilid kedua adalah kisah lanjutan dari novel ringan karangan Mr. Jellyfish yang diilustrasikan oleh Michiryo. Masih menceritakan tentang Elisabeth dan Gabriel, kali ini petualangan keduanya meluas ke kerajaan Wilhemina di barat. Di sana mereka akan terlibat dengan politik dan ikut berperan dalam tragedi yang disebut dengan The Forgotten Queen.</p>\n<h3>The Golden Catalyst</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49878\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49878\" data-attachment-id=\"49878\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lightnovel-id-comic-frontier-11/attachment/04-lightnovel-id-cf11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-lightnovel.id-cf11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49878 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" alt=\"LightNovel.ID golden catalyst\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49878\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: LightNovel.ID</p></div></p>\n<p>Animon Project kembali mengeluarkan karya barunya, kali ini diberi judul the Golden Catalyst. Novel ringan bergenre sains-fiksi aksi ini menceritakan tentang Green, seorang korban dari spesies alien yang disebut dengan nama Katalis. Setelah kedatangan Katalis pada</p>\n<p>tahun 2001, Katalis menjadi ras unggul yang berperan besar dalam perkembangan pesat teknologi dan penghijauan Bumi. Namun di sisi lain, manusia menjadi tumbalnya. Tiap tahunnya manusia dikirim ke pulau Katalis dan dijadikan budak. Green kehilangan kakak dan kedua tangannya. Dengan harapan terakhirnya, Green mencoba untuk memberontak. Namun saat ia mengira dia akan mati, ia bertemu dengan seorang Katalis berwujud manusia yang bersinar keemasan.</p>\n<h3>ALLBLACK</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49879\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49879\" data-attachment-id=\"49879\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lightnovel-id-comic-frontier-11/attachment/05-lightnovel-id-cf11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-lightnovel.id-cf11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49879 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" alt=\"LightNovel.ID allblack\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49879\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: LightNovel.ID</p></div></p>\n<p>Anssen Augustus—pengarang novel ringan sekaligus pendiri dari komunitas LightNovel.ID—akhirnya mengeluarkan jilid kedua dari serial novel ringannya. ALLBLACK jilid kedua menceritakan tentang perjuangan Six, seorang pemuda yang mencari identitasnya setelah ia terbangun di tengah lautan tanpa bisa mengingat apa-apa tentang masa lalunya. Setelah pertempurannya di Mombasa pada jilid sebelumnya, Six singgah di Istanbul dan bertemu dengan Arasaka Yuumi. Ia dijanjikan akan dipertemukan dengan orang yang telah bertanggungjawab atas keadaannya saat ini. Namun di saat yang sama, Six bertemu dengan kawan lamanya yang mengaku telah mencarinya selama 2 tahun belakangan ini. Six pun harus memilih, bagian mana dari masa lalunya yang lebih ingin ia pertahankan. Novel ringan ini</p>\n<p>diilustrasikan oleh Satya Rizqy—Animator dari <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5cE7VtN5z20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Curse of Red Child’s Book</a>—dan Ekki “Ekkigo” Hardiawan yang dikenal mengilustrasikan web novel <a href=\"http://subject09.web.id/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Subject09</a> karangan Bima Ratio.</p>\n<h3>Anchored</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49880\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49880\" data-attachment-id=\"49880\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lightnovel-id-comic-frontier-11/attachment/06-lightnovel-id-cf11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-lightnovel.id-cf11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49880 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg\" alt=\"LightNovel.ID anchored\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-lightnovel.id-cf11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-lightnovel.id-cf11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49880\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: LightNovel.ID</p></div></p>\n<p>Anchored adalah Novel Ringan karangan Aliza Bitthia Dee yang diilustrasikan oleh Nath. Novel ringan ini menceritakan tentang Nerissa, seorang gadis yang seumur hidupnya hidup di bawah lautan. Ia hanya pernah mendengar kisah-kisah tentang dunia di atas permukaan air. Beribu larangan ia dengar dari Ibunya tentang dunia di atas permukaan air, namun rasa penasaran Nerissa tidak terbendung dan akhirnya ia pun membulatkan tekad untuk menyaksikan sendiri dunia yang disembunyikan darinya. Tentunya dengan harga yang tidak sembarangan.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Selain kelima novel ringan yang disebutkan, masih ada beberapa karya lain yang akan ikut mengisi booth LightNovel.ID. Selain ekshibisi karya, LightNovel.ID juga dikabarkan akan menemani Wibuverse naik panggung mengenalkan komunitasnya di hari kedua acara.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"cd4782a9-3f39-5c44-9e99-a6f551c64d9b"}}}